spec_data.Name: golang-github-fortytw2-leaktest-unit-test-devel
spec_data.Description:
Refactored, tested variant of the goroutine leak detector found in
both net/http tests and the cockroachdb source tree.

This package contains unit tests for project
providing packages with github.com/fortytw2/leaktest prefix.
